sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS Reencrypt
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant API as ds-pipeline-api-server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant S3 as S3 Object Store<br/>9000 or 443/TCP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant Pod as Pipeline Pod<br/>(launcher/driver)
    participant MLMD as ds-pipeline-metadata-grpc<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Envoy as ds-pipeline-metadata-envoy<br/>9090/TCP gRPC

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Execution
        User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Route->>Proxy: Forward (TLS Reencrypt)
        Proxy->>Proxy: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(DSPA subresource 'api')
        Proxy->>API: Proxy upstream<br/>TLS (when PodToPodTLS)
        API->>DB: Store run metadata<br/>MySQL TLS (when PodToPodTLS)<br/>Auth: Password (Secret)
        API->>S3: Store pipeline spec<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Auth: AccessKey/SecretKey
        API->>K8s: Create ScheduledWorkflow CR<br/>HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8s-->>Argo: Watch ScheduledWorkflow
        Argo->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        Argo->>Pod: Launch pipeline step pods
        Pod->>MLMD: Record lineage<br/>gRPC mTLS (when PodToPodTLS)
        Pod->>S3: Upload/download artifacts<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Auth: AccessKey/SecretKey
        Pod-->>Argo: Step completion
        Argo-->>API: Workflow status update<br/>(via PersistenceAgent)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over User,DB: Flow 2: MLMD Lineage Query (Dashboard)
        User->>Route: GET MLMD lineage<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Route->>Proxy: Forward (TLS Reencrypt)
        Proxy->>Proxy: SubjectAccessReview
        Proxy->>Envoy: Proxy upstream<br/>plaintext (localhost)
        Envoy->>MLMD: gRPC query<br/>TLS (when PodToPodTLS)
        MLMD->>DB: Query lineage data<br/>MySQL TLS<br/>Auth: Password (Secret)
        DB-->>MLMD: Lineage results
        MLMD-->>Envoy: gRPC response
        Envoy-->>Proxy: Response
        Proxy-->>Route: Response
        Route-->>User: JSON/gRPC Response
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over API,S3: Flow 3: Managed Pipelines Import
        Note right of API: DSPO Controller reconciliation
        API->>S3: Fetch managed-pipelines.json<br/>from OCI registry (443/TCP HTTPS)
        Note right of API: Validate pipeline names<br/>against manifest
        Note right of API: init-managed-pipelines<br/>extracts OCI image layers
        API->>API: Import pipelines from<br/>/config/managed-pipelines/ volume
    end
